      <title>拉詹表示，印度错误地认为增长是“炒作”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/india-making-mistake-believing-hype-about-growth-rajan-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前央行行长拉古拉姆·拉詹表示，印度正在犯下一个大错误，相信其强劲经济增长的“炒作”，因为该国需要解决重大结构性问题才能发挥其潜力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/india-making-mistake-believing-hype-about-growth-rajan-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 07:39:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
