      <title>Ocado 通过降价和促销赢得新客户</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/ocado-wins-over-new-customers-with-price-cuts-and-promotions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Ocado Group Plc 的在线杂货业务销售额增加，因为它降低了价格以吸引刚刚摆脱代际生活成本危机的英国购物者。]]></description>
