      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/catl-chairman-will-keep-expanding-in-the-face-of-slower-ev-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[面对全球电动汽车销售增长放缓，中国世界一流电池制造商的创始人正在大力推进扩张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/catl-chairman-will-keep-expanding-in-the-face-of-slower-ev-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
